            . This Prisoner at the Bar did confess, that he had it, and that he knockt it to Pieces at London Bridge, and after that he sold Part of it, that is the Cog and Plate, for 2 d. a Pound, which weighed 14 lb. and at 2 d. a Pound came to 2 s. 4 d.</p>
